export function getColumnKey(column,defaultKey){if('key'in column&&column.key!==undefined&&column.key!==null){return column.key;}if(column.dataIndex){return Array.isArray(column.dataIndex)?column.dataIndex.join('.'):column.dataIndex;}return defaultKey;}export function getColumnPos(index,pos){return pos?"".concat(pos,"-").concat(index):"".concat(index);}export function renderColumnTitle(title,props){if(typeof title==='function'){return title(props);}return title;}/**
 * Safe get column title
 *
 * Should filter [object Object]
 *
 * @param title
 * @returns
 */export function safeColumnTitle(title,props){const res=renderColumnTitle(title,props);if(Object.prototype.toString.call(res)==='[object Object]')return'';return res;}
